{"tid":369599,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遭黃絲瘋狂洗板   傳真社跪低致歉刪改報道標題內容","createTime":"2017-08-22T12:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-23T09:20:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"61a52230c6dacd1710238d8629dc59794762386e","tid":369599,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:34:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">華文傳媒</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170822/57112214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170822%2F57112214&d=t0vuoKFB%2Bk41C%2BEOXMibUpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=583af627\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170822%2F57112214&h=98f4a7ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170822/57112214</a><br />\n<br />\n民主黨成員林子健早前聲稱在旺角被「強力部門」擄走，其後遭禁錮虐打，大腿更被釘上逾廿口釘，但FactWire《傳真社》後來上載林子健聲稱被擄地點附近的店舖閉路電視片段，證實林的確曾在相關地點出現，其後一名衣著身形與林十分相似的男子中途戴上鴨舌帽、口罩及太陽眼鏡，安全離開旺角，《傳真社》以標題「閉路電視證林子健安全離開砵蘭街 未見有人被擄走 林子健匪夷所思」報道事件。林子健其後被警方以涉嫌誤導警務人員被捕及檢控。<br />\n<br />\n《傳真社》上載的片段在網上引來熱議，有人質疑片段來源及真偽，《傳真社》其後曾上載一篇採訪手記，強調片段是由記者親自向店舖取得。<br />\n<br />\n事隔逾一周，《傳真社》今日上載一篇「報道更正」，指林子健的報道發表至今，收到很多不同意見，當中包含對報道處理手法的批評，稱深切認真地檢討後，承認有關報道的處理不夠審慎，標題及部分內文的用字欠準確，閉路電視顯示的畫面和時間亦應該有更清晰的描述。<br />\n<br />\n《傳真社》將報道標題和部分內容作出更正，並就報道未盡完善致歉。該宗報道標題現已「閉路電視拍得林子健現砵蘭街 其後衣著步姿近似男子戴帽遮面離開 林子健：『匪夷所思』」。而報道內容亦予以刪改，未有再指明戴口罩男子為林子健，而是改以「該男子走過鏡頭前方的路段時，無法見到男子的容貌，但其體型、衣服款式、左手上深色手錶、運動鞋款式、背囊肩帶設計，以至呈內八字的走路姿勢，都與之前拍攝到的林子健十分相似」。<br />\n<br />\n《傳真社》又強調，在整個採訪和報道過程中完全獨立運作，從沒有與任何官方或執法機構接觸，所有閉路電視片段全由記者親自到場向商戶搜集，片段的真偽亦經過嚴謹驗證，並承諾未來處理和發表調查報道時，把關會更嚴謹。"},{"pid":"9ebc1be11a16d970212f82e4149c14d41fbd8eb4","tid":369599,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:35:20.000Z","msg":"呢條先係：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57113737&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170822\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57113737%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170822&d=t0vuoKFB%2Bk41C%2BEOXMibUpUc5Mn1qk%2F8nAzLhrzJJK4%3D&h=a66a11f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57113737%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170822&h=aa948dc4\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57113737&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170822</a>"},{"pid":"490a95ec2f05106ccbbb4b28f2f4fb00b2b82ed5","tid":369599,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170822/large/1503397316_9a0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170822%2Flarge%2F1503397316_9a0b.jpg&h=d8173103&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原圖為傳真社圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170822/large/1503397595_434f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170822%2Flarge%2F1503397595_434f.jpg&h=dbadd38d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《傳真社》有關林子健的報道之標題及內容都已作出更改。"},{"pid":"99cfd3a2def12c4c7eb3f588c4e87b57ce7d2398","tid":369599,"uid":31682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T12:37:36.000Z","msg":"直視暴之根源，別為義人傷悲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/366483?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/366483?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid